{"tid":1716260,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"到呢一刻仲未罷工既你入","createTime":"2019-11-13T09:53:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T11:14:26.000Z","uid":49028,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"036d7831c0a9d3bcad59aed79cac482652f04f46","tid":1716260,"uid":49028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:53:42.000Z","msg":"到底到呢一刻仲想「被罷工」既和理非係咩心態<br />\n係，錢係好重要，可能你要供樓要搵食<br />\n但你有冇諗過，你需要既野，正正就係敵人所需要既野？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>其實港共政府同中共政權比你地更需要錢！</strong></span></span><br />\n你唔返工，係無犯法架，唔通你唔返工會比POPO上門錔你?<br />\n根本呢件事係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">零風險極高回報</span></strong>既行動<br />\n一個社會突然無左<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>２０％勞動人口</strong></span>，已經可以足夠癱瘓啦<br />\n你話你會比人炒，你有冇諗過人地連命都無？<br />\n有命出番來，都有哂案底，冇得走？<br />\n何況當你比人炒，代表左Ｄ咩？<br />\n就係經濟圈重新洗牌！所有人加入黃色經濟圈！<br />\n不單指消費，包括工作，勞動力，集中於同一個經濟圈<br />\n個社會影響力到底有幾高？<br />\n所以政府先一直打壓本土經濟圈，包括領展上市，收緊牌照政策etc<br />\n一件本身可以唔洗用血來換取既事<br />\n到呢一刻死左咁多人，比人恰到上心口<br />\n你地都仲係唔明要點，要後生仔湊住你<br />\n可唔可恥Ｄ呀？<br />\n<br />\n拜託大家，無限期罷工，加入本土黃色經濟圈係唯一勝算<br />\n軍政府無辦法清算你地<br />\n大陸亦無可能有再多資源短時間內去輸入咁多勞動力<br />\n仲要HANDLE到香港文化／工作情況<br />\n呢個係我地唯一可以抗衡既彈藥<br />\n依家係，未來就算正式回歸大陸都係<br />\n既然我地冇辦法用錢來買到子彈<br />\n唯有用錢直接打鳩佢地塊臉！<br />\n<br />\n所以我請求你地，到一刻自問係支持呢場運動既人<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">立即無限期罷工！</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oL5Zdx3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoL5Zdx3.jpg&h=266ef2ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"58c5d93cd03533eb806e162a4b4f638148934ee7","tid":1716260,"uid":49028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:54:07.000Z","msg":"大大力推"},{"pid":"7ed9232219c54914092b14fc154cae1447e71ef3","tid":1716260,"uid":49028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:54:22.000Z","msg":"大大力推"},{"pid":"524d07bc9a5c1c4a7cab5d70de8df6c17c13896c","tid":1716260,"uid":49028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:55:17.000Z","msg":"求你地快啲罷工"},{"pid":"b08a5460a8704e46ab0457a114f288d8f80dd8e3","tid":1716260,"uid":49028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:55:56.000Z","msg":"救下我地嘅學生 救下個社會"},{"pid":"a423bccbd30de8ad5cfa2e4874ebfbc4cc592dcb","tid":1716260,"uid":49028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:56:14.000Z","msg":"多你一個好撚多"},{"pid":"cfa9f79bfcabdfabb9d57b49dca91ab6bc1b5885","tid":1716260,"uid":49028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:56:54.000Z","msg":"推比未罷嘅人睇"},{"pid":"a3c9fa4ba774a8fdbba90945abc078e1eb18c2e1","tid":1716260,"uid":49028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:57:10.000Z","msg":"求你"},{"pid":"b58c4d61d2bbb77adf54f5124b7e898e874b77d4","tid":1716260,"uid":49028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:58:32.000Z","msg":"今日未開始唔緊要<br />\n今晚zip高枕頭諗諗佢"},{"pid":"26a121e92e048edbac7603739db73eb57379c933","tid":1716260,"uid":49028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:59:09.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"1f75cae57a469a413735e17b14417b18e83d196a","tid":1716260,"uid":49028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:59:19.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"b248ccf47d2e57617e97ddcb0a58f8022c8a5697","tid":1716260,"uid":49028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:59:45.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"37fa3175ee374b09bf3ea98da039eca2dd9fe065","tid":1716260,"uid":49028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T10:00:02.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"dc10d2708247d04077b55ceae339cbfc0fb8e652","tid":1716260,"uid":49028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T10:00:26.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"e0ccf0eafb2b0ac9e2733388a09e8160ee2caa6e","tid":1716260,"uid":49028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T10:00:38.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"4